a.n: World Grand Prix Fight TNA, 1/8th finals, TATNEFT CUP, Tatneft Arena, Kazan, Russia

p.d: The second stage of the 1/8th finals of the "TATNEFT CUP" tournament, which took place in Kazan (Russia), at the "Tatneft Arena" in Ice Sports Palace. Six bouts are scheduled for the event in three weight categories involving fighters from China, Russia, Albania, Romania, Belarus, France, and Italy.
